## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023, and the situation regarding COVID-19 is continually evolving. The findings are subject to change as new data emerges. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may have their own limitations in terms of data collection and analysis. The impact of COVID-19 may vary significantly across different regions and populations, which may not be fully captured in this report.

